@MissionCtrlApi_HostAddress = http://localhost:5242

### Get all mission tasks
GET {{MissionCtrlApi_HostAddress}}/api/missionTasks
Accept: application/json

### Get single mission task
GET {{MissionCtrlApi_HostAddress}}/api/missionTasks/1
Accept: application/json

### Create new mission task
POST {{MissionCtrlApi_HostAddress}}/api/missionTasks
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Test Mission Task",
  "description": "This is a test mission task",
  "status": "Pending",
  "dueDate": "2026-12-31"
}

### Update mission task
PUT {{MissionCtrlApi_HostAddress}}/api/missionTasks/1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Updated Mission Task",
  "description": "This mission task has been updated",
  "status": "InProgress",
  "dueDate": "2026-12-31"
}

### Delete mission task
DELETE {{MissionCtrlApi_HostAddress}}/api/missionTasks/1

###
